    "content": [
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Why I Switched to BugHerd for Website Feedback",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I used to collect website feedback through screenshots in Slack, screenshots attached to emails, and screenshots buried in Google Drive folders. Clients would describe problems like \"the thing on the right side looks weird\" and I'd spend 20 minutes figuring out what they meant.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "BugHerd changed that completely. Instead of screenshots and vague descriptions, my clients point directly at the issue on the live website, leave a comment, and BugHerd captures everything—the exact element, the browser details, the screen resolution. One click, done.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you build websites for clients or manage a team that does, this tutorial will walk you through exactly how to set up and use BugHerd to collect feedback without the chaos.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What BugHerd Actually Does (In Plain English)",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l0",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/what-is-bugherd"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "BugHerd is a ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "visual website feedback tool",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " that works like sticky notes on a live website. Here's the core concept:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Your client opens the staging site (or live site)",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "They click on any element they want to comment on",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "A pin drops and a comment box appears",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "BugHerd automatically grabs a screenshot, the CSS selector, browser info, and OS details",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "That feedback becomes a task in your BugHerd board",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "No extensions needed for your clients. No training sessions. No \"please take a screenshot and circle the problem.\" Just point, click, comment.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l1",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/why-choose-bugherd"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Want to see why teams keep choosing it? Check out ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "why BugHerd stands out",
            "marks": [
              "l1"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " for website projects.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Step 1: Create Your BugHerd Account",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l2",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://partners.bugherd.com/tj7d6g9xsdd0"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Head to ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "BugHerd's website",
            "marks": [
              "l2"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " and sign up. You can use Google SSO or create an account with email. Here's what I appreciate: no credit card required upfront. You get a 60-day money-back guarantee, so there's zero risk in trying it with a real project.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Once you're in, you'll land on the dashboard. BugHerd uses a Kanban-style board by default—columns like \"New,\" \"In Progress,\" \"Done\"—but you can customize these to match your workflow.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Pro tip:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Spend two minutes setting up your columns before adding your first project. It saves time later when feedback starts rolling in.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Step 2: Install BugHerd on Your Website",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This is where BugHerd's simplicity shines. You install a small JavaScript snippet on your website, similar to adding Google Analytics. That's it.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Here's the process:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "1. In your BugHerd dashboard, click \"Add a Project\"",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "2. Enter your website URL",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "3. Copy the provided script tag",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "4. Paste it before the closing `</body>` tag on your site",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "5. Refresh your site and confirm the BugHerd sidebar appears",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "For WordPress sites, you can use a plugin. For sites built on frameworks like React or Next.js, just add the script to your main layout file.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The whole installation takes about 3 minutes. I've timed it.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Step 3: Invite Your Team and Clients",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "BugHerd has two types of users: ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "members",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " (your team who manage tasks) and ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "guests",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " (clients or stakeholders who leave feedback).",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Members",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " get full access to the task board, can assign work, change statuses, and manage the project",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Guests",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " only see the feedback sidebar on the website—they can point, click, and comment, but they don't access your internal task board",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This separation is brilliant. Your client never sees internal notes like \"client doesn't understand responsive design\" or priority labels. They just see a clean interface for leaving feedback.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Invite team members from Settings → Members. Send guest links from Settings → Guests. Guests don't need to create an account—they click a link and start annotating.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l3",
            "_type": "link",
