        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This automatic context is a massive time-saver. Instead of asking \"which browser are you using?\" or \"can you send me a screenshot?\"—you already have everything.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I once had a client report a \"broken button\" that only appeared broken on Safari 15. Without BugHerd's automatic browser detection, I would have spent an hour trying to reproduce it in Chrome.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
